---
import ServiceIcon from '@assets/icons/service-line.svg';
---

<section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 sm:gap-16">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <ServiceIcon class="fill-primary-500 h-8 w-8 shrink-0 sm:h-10 sm:w-10" aria-hidden="true" />
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">How I Work</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="bg-surface flex flex-col gap-12 rounded-3xl px-6 py-8 backdrop-blur-md">
          <p class="text-sm">01</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Deep Experience</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">15+ years shipping production software across the stack — web, mobile, desktop, and enterprise. Seasoned engineering judgment to guide every project.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface flex flex-col gap-12 rounded-3xl px-6 py-8 backdrop-blur-md">
          <p class="text-sm">02</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">AI-Accelerated</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">Local LLM environments (Ollama, OpenCode, Claude Code) with structured prompting and context-management workflows. Model evaluation for code quality and task fit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface flex flex-col gap-12 rounded-3xl px-6 py-8 backdrop-blur-md">
          <p class="text-sm">03</p>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-medium">Production-Ready</h3>
            <p class="text-muted text-base sm:text-lg">Technical audits, structured milestones, and recovery sprints ensure every deliverable meets production standards. No shortcuts on quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
